分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n經過炒炸的臭屁蟲會變得非常香脆可口，有食客更介紹可添加杜仲、豬尾、五指毛桃、陳皮等藥材煲湯，更加美味。"},{"pid":"3c0cef4f1baca13b5dfa91fd677d95591918ed55","tid":1085294,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T05:09:18.000Z","msg":"又有龍珠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49881c8e46a8ecab928c81a26a217fc17ec278fb","tid":1085294,"uid":68128,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T05:10:18.000Z","msg":"又話無圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eba77db0acaf309709ca6c1b6df6e4b3f24c5c35","tid":1085294,"uid":51746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T05:12:31.000Z","msg":"樓主仆街啦佢地生長速度用次方計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔計呀爸呀媽下一輪有196隻蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"954dde95c8b1997f9b17a34752326b4784fb419c","tid":1085294,"uid":190957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T05:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0708b930337732229958063ef426918b9c0121b4","tid":1085294,"uid":190957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a6a94b10f8f134fd6e3d3b1a46a44a33d8d063fa","tid":1085294,"uid":155431,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T05:08:00.000Z","msg":"要整爆佢，如果唔係會生蟲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T05:13:22.000Z","msg":"唔敢行近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd9761e774d4211e25967dcf803fa5e10d0f6ad1","tid":1085294,"uid":159659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T05:14:38.000Z","msg":"唔可以行近，臭屁蟲老母見到有人整自己d蛋會飛出黎噴毒汁"},{"pid":"d92138acd7836ecb6e03447179a74bc5eb649c10","tid":1085294,"uid":190957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd9761e774d4211e25967dcf803fa5e10d0f6ad1","tid":1085294,"uid":159659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-